title: Michel Foucault's Discipline and Punish
description:
This is my first upload, so have patience if something goes wrong. I couldn't find a good version of this anywhere online so I scanned it myself (for those like me who need to be able to cite page numbers). I made it fairly large so that it's OCRable. I'm going to scan Dialectic of Enlightenment next if anyone's interested in that. BTW it took me forever to find a good pdf editor - of the ones I tried (pretty much everything available except Adobe Acrobat) Nitro Professional is awesome and everything else sucks. I think this is the version I used:.

Autumn
